               <p>Mr. Baldwin. What is the form of the oath? - The executor laying his hand on the Bible, swears that is the last will and testament of such a one, and that he is the sole executor therein named.</p>
               <p>Court. Write me down the words of the oath, as the Doctor mentions it, I only want it for the Jury.</p>
